              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14392286887150801107">I love Alice Hoffman and it pains me to say that I didn&apos;t like this book. I wish there was &quot;It was ok&quot; star. The writing itself is beautiful; she writes like no other. I did not believe her characters. I couldn&apos;t figure out who they were or really, why I should care about them. I love you, Alice - just not this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText14392286887150801107" style="display:none">I love Alice Hoffman and it pains me to say that I didn't like this book. I wish there was "It was ok" star. The writing itself is beautiful; she writes like no other. I did not believe her characters. I couldn't figure out who they were or really, why I should care about them. I love you, Alice - just not this book.</span>
